06:39.640 --> 06:41.165
Just forget it happened.

07:08.280 --> 07:11.011
Norman?
Excuse me, Norman.

07:11.760 --> 07:13.410
What is going on?

07:14.160 --> 07:15.730
I have to leave.
Why?

07:17.920 --> 07:19.126
I just have to.

07:19.200 --> 07:20.770
Well, do you have a note?

07:20.840 --> 07:22.251
You have to
have a note.

07:22.320 --> 07:24.448
Norman, you cannot just walk
away from school and leave.

07:25.320 --> 07:27.129
You'll get cited.
You'll get suspended.

07:27.200 --> 07:29.009
I don't care!

07:30.880 --> 07:34.851
Norman. Just come back
inside, and we can...

07:38.520 --> 07:41.046
