got shot here.

08:37.720 --> 08:39.609
Right up there,
on those steps.

08:46.320 --> 08:47.765
Yeah, he did.

08:48.760 --> 08:50.808
It's funny.
You never know someone.

08:52.320 --> 08:56.928
I knew Keith Summers all these years.
Not well, but I knew him.

08:58.360 --> 09:01.125
And here he was.
He's in the motel for this...

09:02.760 --> 09:03.921
sex trade.

09:05.360 --> 09:07.124
You just never know,
do you?

09:17.160 --> 09:19.845
Yeah, I guess you don't.

09:20.440 --> 09:22.044
(GASPS) on!
(GLASS SHATTERS)

09:22.160 --> 09:23.321
(SIGHS)

09:23.520 --> 09:27.809
Sorry about that. I'll grab
a bulb from another room.

09:32.120 --> 09:33.690
It's no worries.

09:37.600 --> 09:39.250
Did you know Zack Shelby?

09:41.000 --> 09:42.445
Did I know him?

09:44.520 --> 09:47.524
A little. I guess like how
you knew Keith Summers.

09:48.960 --> 09:50.371
So not so much?

09:52.120 --> 09:53.531
No, not so much.

10:02.720 --> 10:05.007
I'm sorry. I have to, um...
I just remembered.

10:05.080 --> 10:06.366
I have to give my son
a ride somewhere.

10:07.000 --> 10:08.843
He's not here. Yeah.

10:09.640 --> 10:11.369
Yeah, I saw him leave.

10:13.080 --> 10:14.206
School, wasn't it?

10:17.480 --> 10:19.881
I got to go.
I'm gonna come back

10:19.960 --> 10:21.849
and I'll finish up later,
okay?

10:30.520 --> 10:32.124
I just... Just...

10:36.000 --> 10:37.286
We're good for now.

10:45.400 --> 10:47.687
If I need anything else
I'll come by the office.

10:47.760 --> 10:48.807
Sure.

10:58.760 --> 10:59.921
REGINA: Mmm-hmm.

11:02.760 --> 11:04.091
Sheriff Romero
can see you now.

11:05.600 --> 11:07.523
So what can I help
you with, Mrs. Bates?

11:07.600 --> 11:11.241
Oh, please, call me Norma, after
everything we've been through.

11:13.920 --> 11:15.922
You know that I called
your office this morning.

11:16.600 --> 11:17.806
You know, I was coming
in town anyway.

11:17.880 --> 11:20.281
I thought, oh, I'll just
pop in and see him.

11:23.560 --> 11:25.164
So anyway, um...

11:27.120 --> 11:28.849
You know, I bought the
motel a few months ago,

11:28.920 --> 11:31.730
and no one told me
at the time

11:31.800 --> 11:33.962
