on building a new bypass

11:34.040 --> 11:36.884
that would basically
take my motel off the map.

11:37.880 --> 11:38.961
Mmm-hmm.

11:39.960 --> 11:44.329
So I'm just trying to
figure out a way that, um,

11:44.400 --> 11:46.482
