for political favors based on nothing.

13:27.680 --> 13:29.330
You and I have
no connection.

13:30.280 --> 13:32.248
We're not on the same
playing field.

13:32.320 --> 13:33.606
Don't ever assume
that we are.

13:38.080 --> 13:39.809
You don't know
what you're doing.

13:42.360 --> 13:43.566
Go home, Mrs. Bates.

13:50.040 --> 13:51.530
