13:53.840 --> 13:55.683
Hello?
HUDGINS: <i>Mrs. Bates?</i>

13:55.960 --> 13:57.121
Yes.

13:57.240 --> 13:58.321
<i>This is Tom Hudgins.</i>

13:58.440 --> 14:01.091
<i>I'm the principal of
White Pine Bay High School.</i>

14:01.160 --> 14:03.208
<i>We'd like you to come
in this afternoon.</i>

14:03.320 --> 14:06.085
<i>We need to discuss your
son's behavior at school.</i>

14:17.000 --> 14:19.765
