much with others.

16:25.560 --> 16:26.686
He keeps to himself a lot.

16:28.240 --> 16:30.891
And based on the behavior
that I have seen,

16:31.240 --> 16:33.004
Principal Hudgins
and I would like

16:33.080 --> 16:34.730
